lead_paragraph: Sevilla midfielder Samir Nasri has been ruled out of this week's Champions League game against Dinamo Zagreb with a muscle injury, the club said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Sevilla's Nasri Ruled Out of Zagreb Match
